Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在面臨能源危機  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got an energy crisis, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮應該...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now what the White House needs to --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統選擇對中國保持強硬態度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president chose to remain tough on China.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是被你逼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. You forced him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇了馮  是你讓我和他見面的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You chose Feng. You're the one who put me in a room with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廚子手藝不好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The cook can't blame his ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能去怪原料差\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he doesn't like how they taste together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果釤的價格不降\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If Samarium prices don't reduce,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市場只能隨之上調電價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the market will have no choice but to compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣對每一個使用空調的人來說都是壞訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's bad for everyone who owns an air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該去找總統本人談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should speak to the president himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統最近不是很重視我的意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the president hasn't placed much value on my advice lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm in the same boat as you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同的是  你和他的辦公室只隔三道門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Difference being you've got an office three doors down from the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們同心協力吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's work together, for Christ sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你願意  我可以忘記斯波特瑟爾維尼亞的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm wiling to put Spotsylvania behind us if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你會去跟他談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you'll talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開會要遲到了  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm late for a meeting, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答應還是不答應  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes or no, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能保證他聽得進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't guarantee he'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是答應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比不答應強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it's better than a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱職的拳擊手都能看出對手什麼時候不行了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any pugilist worth his salt knows when someone's on the ropes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候就該果斷連續出拳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's when you throw a combination to the gut
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左勾拳直擊下顎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and a left hook to the jaw.
