Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釤的價格他們絕不會讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Samarium is the last thing they'll let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能源價格一直漲  他們就有談判籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As long as our energy prices rise, they have the leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們只是靜觀其變呢  跟他們比瞪眼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't we offer nothing? Move toward attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果中國不參加再融資債券拍賣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If China doesn't show at the refunding auction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長期利率會一路飆升\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}long-term interest rates will spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期後我們的十年期國債\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And in a week yields on our 10-year notes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將突破7%大關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will pierce the seven-percent threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是有可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們現在妥協  那就是必然了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if we go soft now, that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我們應該強硬一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少應該考慮一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should at least consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人不吃敬酒  我們就上罰酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Chinese don't like carrots. Let's see how they like the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, what might that look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增加糧食檢查的頻率\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We could raise inspection rates on foodstuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們的糧食扣在港口直到腐爛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold them in our ports till they rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提高多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much of a raise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要有效果要提高20%\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}20% if we want to draw blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用增加抽查次數的方式進行掩飾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bury the move with increased spot checks all the way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這類措施不能解決眼前的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These sort of tactics don't solve the immediate problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們現在交著三倍的電費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People are paying triple the standard rate for electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到八月份  就是五倍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll hit a five-fold increase by August.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你  總統先生  通過行政命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if you, Mr. President, by executive order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第三方手裡購買釤呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}purchase Samarium through a third party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞過中國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cut the Chinese out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫使他們提高全球價格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Force them to either raise their prices worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是降低價格維持跟我們的交易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or lower them to keep direct flow with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  對外宣稱是為了國防需要進行釤儲備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We stockpile Samarium for denfense purposes, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後悄悄的把多餘的釤賣給我們核能源方面的盟友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And quietly sell what we don't need to our friends in nuclear energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以優惠價格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核能源補助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A subsidy for nuclear power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有錢人相互接濟  這別人會怎麼看啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The richest of the rich? How's that gonna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在面對國家危機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're dealing with a national crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能受公眾輿論的影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't get sidetracked with public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這能讓中國知道我們願意耐心等待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It would show China we're willing to wait this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有這份錢嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do we have the resources?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要計算一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd have to run the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預期波動  考慮不同模式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}anticipate fluctuations, consider different models --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估計一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your best guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有  可以進行中度儲備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We do. For a moderate stockpile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好  以國防部名義起草請求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. Draw up a request from the Defense Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是  先生    -琳達  起草行政命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir.    - Linda, draft the executive order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜  確保我們能找到一個第三方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Cathy, make sure we have a third-party conduit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,購買釤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to purchase the Samarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟印度買吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll go through India.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那巴基斯坦可要不高興了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that won't fly well with Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會提前告知他們  只要及時告知他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll alert them in advance. As long as they're in the loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼問題  我們又不欠他們什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'll be all right. Not that we owe them any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好  開始工作吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝茜  還加上E條款下的三條罪名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, Betsy. Three additional counts under Section E?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三條已經很少了  反映了對犯罪意圖的狹義解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Three is low. It reflects a narrow interpretation of criminal intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的委託人入侵了資料中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your client broke into a data center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:05:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能提供什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會認罪的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not doing a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來處理這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不想開庭審判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They don't want a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能在公開法庭上高聲提出的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The questions I'll be raising loud and clear in open court...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯  別這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有問題  古德溫先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have our own questions, Mr. Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如  你怎麼會有這些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For example, what were you doing with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我拍的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在你公寓發現的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They were in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德拍的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Underwood took them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得陪審團能信嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you really expect a jury to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他  他們有一腿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He did. They were having an affair --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只會如實看待這些證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or are they gonna see them for what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你迷戀巴恩斯女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Proof of our obsession with Ms. Barnes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還編出一套荒唐的陰謀論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the ludicrous conspiracy you have concocted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來解釋她的死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to explain her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell us what you're offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你委託人供認以下罪名  E條款下一條\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your client pleads to one count under Section E
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闖入資料中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for breaking into a data center,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺詐一條  偷《先驅報》的密碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}one count for fraud, for stealing the password from the Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一項獲罪10年  第二項10年  同時計算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}10 years under Section E. 10 years for fraud. Served concurrently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服刑7年可假釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Eligible for parole in seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想單獨跟委託人談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to speak to my client, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請關掉錄影錄音裝置\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cameras and recording equipment off, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我介紹總統  他來介紹你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll introduce the president, then he'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在  就不能點名軍方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he's there, we can't mention the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能說全國皆有這種現象\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just the endemic problem nationwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那再過一遍講詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good. So we should go through these speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看還有沒有...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and make sure that there's nothing --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hi, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃剋夫人  你找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Walker, you asked for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要確認一下總統能不能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to confirm whether the president's going
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去新奧爾良\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to make it to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這週五吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This Friday, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  但我知道他今早有內閣會議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. But I know he had a cabinet meeting this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so I imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去和琳達溝通一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to Linda right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你希望加勒特去  可能源危機的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you want Garrett there. But with this energy crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下你非說不可了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, now you have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是向來不太喜歡克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've just never been very fond of her. Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼得·羅素\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Peter Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不太喜歡跟老闆上床的女人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just have a thing about women who sleep with their bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我相信他們是真心相愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyway, I'm sure whatever they had was genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不關我事  只要她工作做得好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's none of my business, 'cause if she's doing a good job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他也無所謂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's all that matters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特還挺滿意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett seems to think she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不多嘴了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I should just keep my feelings to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果總統不能去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So if the president is not able to be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對咱們或許也是好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that could be a silver lining for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用給軍方留面子了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We won't have to hold back with the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話監聽  視訊監控  預謀犯罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Phone taps. Video surveillance. Premeditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長期動機  你沒希望的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sustained intent. They've got you cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我認罪  就沒人知道真相了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I plead out, that's it. No one hears the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不認罪的話  根本沒人會聽你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you don't plead, no one will hear you, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到你七八十歲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not until you're in your 70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和漢默施密特談了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you talked to Hammerschmidt yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格談條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're in no position to make demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說了又不算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只會惹惱他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you'll do is piss them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個交易很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we've got a good deal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到你的行為  算很不錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A great deal, considering what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁他們沒改主意  趕緊接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should take it before their change their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆·漢默施密特  我要跟他談  否則就上法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tom Hammerschmidt. I talk to him, or we're going to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請擡起胳膊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raise your arms, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有什麼物品\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,項鍊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My neck chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請掏出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  我還得解領帶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Really? I gotta take off my tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須看一下  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to see it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虔誠的基督徒啊  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a good Christian, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我母親的  是她虔誠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My mother's. She was the good Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你也是個好兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, then you're just the good son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面熱吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hot out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,96華氏度  車裡顯示的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}96, according to my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前在加夫尼也這麼熱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We had heat like that back in Gaffney,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會兒還沒有空調\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we didn't know what air conditioning was,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為夏天就該這麼難熬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so we just accepted as fact that summer was meant to be miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加不加水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Neat or with water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要水  不要酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just the water. You can hold the bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得找個解決辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這個夏天美國人民不那麼難熬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that this one isn't miserable for 300 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有辦法了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already have found a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧  弗蘭克  釤補助嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, please, Frank. A Samarium subsidy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你還是雷蒙德表示懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that your skepticism or Raymond's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  估計他也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mine. Anticipating his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倆還沒談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you haven't spoken to him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想向他提出他會同意的條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to offer him something he can agree to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒什麼選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he doesn't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要把他逼入絕境\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why are you cornering him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把價錢減半  這是在幫他啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm cutting the rate by half. I'd call that liberating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他可不這麼看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know that's not how he'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場貿易戰讓北京方面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This trade war is preventing the refinery
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲遲不批准精煉廠項目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from being approved in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前  他跟馮的合資項目不是最重要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His co-venture with Feng is not our highest priority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稀土精煉廠能一勞永逸地解決這場危機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A rare earth refinery solves this crisis permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是三年之後了  這個夏天還是難熬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Three years from now. Not this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此  實施核能補助他至多不賠不賺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not just that. With the subsidy he'll break even at best,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫做生意嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there's no point in doing business to hover between red and black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德的利益對我來說比他的合資項目更不重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond's profits are an even lower priority to me than his co-venture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你的目的  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you're up to, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟塔斯克叫勁又得不到什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's nothing to gain by locking horn with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問你的客戶去  是塔斯克在叫勁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ask your client. It's Tusk who's locking the horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不喜歡矛盾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's not a man who likes conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就提出要求吧  我知道你不在乎核能補助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then make the ask. 'Cause I know you don't care about the subsidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有更大的目標\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個虔誠的基督徒  雷米  跟你母親一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a good Christian, Remy, like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想要別的  我會如實說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would tell you the truth if I wanted more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在發出訊號嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You trying to send a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那內容是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頑固比順從的代價更大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That stubbornness is far more costly than obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你站錯隊了  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're on the wrong side, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我們中肯定有一人站錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, one of us sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大黃蜂飛回家後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when the bumblebee flew home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現它的朋友們都抱著大桶蜂蜜在等他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}all his friends were waiting with buckets honey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的朋友有蠕蟲  老鼠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he's got his worm friend and his mouse friend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛和蝸牛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and his spider friend and his snail friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們都有許多蜂蜜  他看上去開心多了  是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And they all had tons of honey. And he looks happier now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是啊    -是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yeah!   - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是他們開心地嗡嗡叫了起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And so they all buzzzzed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和朋友們在一起  生活會甜蜜得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because life is sweet when you spend it with your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們會振動翅膀發出嗡鳴聲嗎  扇動小翅膀吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you all buzz your wings? Buzz your little wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我覺得會發出顫動的聲音  就像    -就像\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I think it would make a fluttering noise, like...   - like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的顫動呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your flutters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面太熱了  你不該拋球  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's too hot out here for you to be doing this, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在喝水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm keeping hydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這距離滿足規定嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that even regulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只到一半\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's only half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想讓媒體看到我在大街上練習\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I don't want the press to see practicing on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你在格林維爾開球那次嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You remember when you threw out that first pitch in Greenville?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想你什麼時候會提到那事呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was wondering how long it was gonna take you to bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次還不是全國電視臺直播呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That wasn't even on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格林維爾發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened in Greenville?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格林維爾驅動隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Greenville Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅襪隊的1A隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Single A team for the Red Sox.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主場作戰  我站在投球區土墩上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a home game. I get on the mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從土墩上拋球嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You threw from the mound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想投個好球\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I wanted to throw a real pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒拋好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差得遠呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一半嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Halfway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球在我鬆手前滑了出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ball slipped out of my hand just before I released it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直線拋上了天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Went straight up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來砸在我頭上  全場爆發大笑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hit me on top of the head. The whole stadium burst a gut laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜劇性投球\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Comic relief pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會說話  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's very clever, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't tell Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他們處的真好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're really good with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們作手指畫時  你看到羅比了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you see Robbie when they were finger-painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他脫掉了褲子  把他自己塗成藍色\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He pulled down his pants and started painting himself blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒看到    -真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願我都洗乾淨了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hope I got it all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾利克斯和達利爾不會在意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure Alex and Daria don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們總是讓他光著身子四處跑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They let him run around naked all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  但不會像光屁股的藍精靈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but probably not with his Smurf ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們今晚吃什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do we want to do for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一些吃剩的雞肉  或者我們可以叫披薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got some leftover chicken. Or we could order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,披薩  不做菜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pizza. No dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘了有個朋友今晚要來接我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I totally forgot I've got a friend picking me up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I completely blanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒事    -我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- That's fine.   - I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必道歉  是你男朋友嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't sweat it. Is it, uh, your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是一個老朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no. Um, just an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能見見他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有點害羞  我不知道他是否願意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he's kinda shy. I do-- I don't know if he'd be up for --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Totally cool. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們改天再一起吃晚飯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll just do dinner another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你知道去哪裡找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You know where I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多久了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾個月了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去教堂嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't go to church?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟任何人有接觸都可能暴露我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anywhere you interact with other people opens us up to risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就該整天悶在呼叫中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right. I'm just supposed to slave away at the fucking call center
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是待在公寓裡不出來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and then lock myself in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼小題大做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't get dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這些人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎  沒有什麼可擔心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay? There -- there's nothing to worry about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果誰林奇堡的親戚來訪就能毀了一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All it takes is one person's cousin to visit from Lynchburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是你的高中同學\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone you went to high school with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是曾跟你共度良宵的客戶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or some client that you spend the night with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人才不會出現在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those guys would never end up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不就跑來這裡了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You ended up here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這麼生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這麼生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你能  你是個堅強的姑娘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you can. You're a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些  這就是全部了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's it? That's everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你以前就聽過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know. You've heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為一個朋友  盧卡斯  而不是記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As a friend, Lucas. Not as a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會接著挖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去打電話  去跑腿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I make the phone calls. I do the legwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們對你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They treating you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們非常想達成認罪協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're pushing the plea deal pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在認真考慮嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How seriously are you considering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看文章的影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to see how this article impacts things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的律師怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What does your lawyer say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他覺得這是個壞主意  我應該認罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He thinks that's a bad idea. That I should take the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許你應該聽他的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe you should listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要文章  我確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I want the article. That I'm certain of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我得趕快開始了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. I better get to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會像對待其他報道一樣對待這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna treat this the way I would any other story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報道事實  你也許不會喜歡我寫的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever the facts bear. You might not like what I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會先讓你看  然後你再做決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you read it first. Then you can decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我擦掉嗎  求你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you wipe this off? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他核供應商都贊同嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the other nuclear providers are on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部分  除了雷蒙德的公司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most. Except Raymond's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Couple of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖港核電站  狼泉集團\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lakeport Nuclear. Wolf Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法證明  但我敢肯定他們是串通好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, I can't prove it, but I am absolutely sure they're colluding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德想讓我丟臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond wants to embarrass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提出方案  核能說客卻不肯合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I offer a solution, nuclear lobby turns its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有拒絕的權利  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He has the right to refuse, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他沒法操縱能源市場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What he cannot do is manipulate the energy market.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對經銷方施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to put pressure on the distribution side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅施壓  徹底禁止縱向合併\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than pressure. Ban vertical integration entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有那個管制權力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't have that regulatory power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給《緊急能源法案》加一條反壟斷協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We add an antitrust agreement to the Emergency Energy Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們打破地區性供應和經銷壟斷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We break up the regional supply and distribution monopolies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像當年對貝爾系統那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like the Bell System.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs14\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}1984年  司法部結束了貝爾公司對電話服務的壟斷  將一個大公司拆分為獨立小公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那馬上就會引起官司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It'll be challenged immediately in the courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要協議通過  只是用來嚇唬人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't need it to pass. We just need to threaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他會不會屈服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See if he falls into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事能不能低調辦妥  不鬧上新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there a way to do that without it making its way into the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望世界上最有錢的有錢人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want the world's wealthiest one percent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都給我打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on my phone sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is absolutely a way to do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的酒來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,週二晚上就這麼熱鬧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Crowded for a Tuesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們把室溫保持在18度  而且免費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We keep it at 65 degrees. And it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一杯伏特加蘇打水18塊也叫免費嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you call 18 bucks for a vodka soda free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也比電力公司的賬單便宜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Still cheaper than a Pepco bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要看你喝多少了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Depends on how many you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我們喝醉嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You trying to get us drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝得越醉  給的小費越多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Drunker you are, bigger your tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用喝醉就會好好答謝優質服務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't have to be drunk to appreciate good service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找零錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll get your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真不要臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是個好說客  乾杯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Makes me a good lobbyist. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬  舉動很大膽  但是沒用的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, Jackie, bold move, but it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們可以輕鬆通過這項修正案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know we can pass this amendment in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許  但沒有人會遵守\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe. But no one'll comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它會被推翻  最後竹籃打水一場空\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It'll get overturned. Big fuss for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會被推翻  但依然會留下印記\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might get overturned. But it gets ink along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我對雷蒙德·塔斯克的瞭解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One thing I learned about Raymond Tusk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他才不在乎什麼公眾意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is he doesn't two bird shits about public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的股東們在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His stockholders do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他一句話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'd jump in a pit of snakes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會跳進蛇窩  把自己點燃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and light themselves on fire if he gave the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你能轉達我們的意圖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I'm asking if that you convey our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼找我  弗蘭克打個電話還不容易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why me? Frank could easily pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還叫他弗蘭克呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You still call him Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會當面叫  我也儘量避免見他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not to his face, which I try to keep to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得在白宮有個能說上話的人很好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't you appreciate having an ear in the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣還好了  但最近我淨聽他說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't, if I had an ear. But lately all I've got is a mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他不是很善於傾聽  對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. He's not the best listener, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是為他工作就知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Try working for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在他手下幹過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were on his staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八年  新聞發言人  那時你還沒進入國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Eight years. Press secretary. Before you joined Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒說明了很多問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That explains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如很多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就當你是在羞辱我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll take that as an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就走嗎  這就撇下我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's it? You're abandoning me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我去買下一輪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I'm buying the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮尚往來嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't accept gifts from lobbyists without reciprocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是個好幫手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Plus, I'm a good wingman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你能多跟那個酒吧女侍接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This gets you more face time with the barmaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗萊迪燒烤餐館
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都做好了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You already got 'em ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下通知我你要來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your guys gave me the heads-up you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們沒有太早吵醒你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I hope that they didn't wake you earlier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操  這麼熱我哪能睡得著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fuck, man. With this heat I ain't sleeping much anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  家裡沒有空調嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What? No AC at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有空調  只是不想付賬單\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I got a unit. I just don't want to pay the damn bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總的來說  這裡的溫度還可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not too bad in here, all things considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我們在陰涼處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's 'cause we in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過兩小時  你要是去外面人行道上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you get outside a couple hours from now on that pavement,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾燙的地面能把你的雞巴烤熟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}fry your damn dick off from three feet below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燒烤架那邊一定很難熬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Must be bad over that grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都覺不出區別了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't tell the difference no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我跟你說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tell you what, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣溫超過37度  這裡的情況就會變糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stuff goes down aroundhere when the mercury pop a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在家裡打老婆的男人會到街上來打\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Man who beat his wife at home will beat her right out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的獸性都暴露出來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Brings out the animal in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是開玩笑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It ain't no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我會被什麼驚醒  槍聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What used to wake me up? Gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在是什麼嗎  人們操的聲音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you know what does? People fucking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是呻吟又是尖叫  像巷子裡的貓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Moaning and screaming like god damn cats in the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說得好  天熱一身汗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know what they say: When you get hot and sweaty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫衣就開幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it make you ripe and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都喝多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We both did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的事沒發生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Last night didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門之後  一切公事公辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I walk out that door, it's business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特殊優待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  你不需要申請禁制令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. You won't need a restraining order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很驚訝  你沒去找那個女招待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised you didn't go for the waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比她性感得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're much sexier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為小費工作  而你運作國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She works for tips. You run Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一半\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也比她厲害得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's half more than she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不是我的身體吸引你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So it's not my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雙腿還是挺不錯的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those legs don't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是滿口胡言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're so full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  是你的聲音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. It's your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我欲罷不能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It does something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把塔斯克的意思轉達給我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me know what Tusk has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不談公事  你還沒出門呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Business hasn't started. You haven't walked out that door yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷米·丹頓  \N公事：跟雷·塔談過了  他說法庭上見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're going to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小約翰在移動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Little John on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們提高賭注  把聯邦能源管理委員會拉進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We raise the bet. We get FERC involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要國會來呼叫能源委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't need Congress to activate the Regulatory Commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是價格聽證  會耗費好幾個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But a price-fixing review? That would take months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說一次  只是威脅  不是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Again, it's the threat. Not the actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會採用同樣的對策\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll employ the same logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這事拿到法庭上去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Draw it out. Fight back with appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果聯邦能源管理委員會開始行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he'll have to divulge his accounting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的賬目就會曝光\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if FERC takes action.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哪個生意人願意公開賬目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, no businessman wants to open up his books,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是430億的賬目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}especially one with $43 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事開始失控了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is getting outta hand, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不應該跟雷蒙德對著幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We shouldn't be duking it out with Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們該和他談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是他想要的  讓自己回到圈裡來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what he wants. To force himself back into the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他排除在外有什麼好處呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's to be gained by shutting him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他個教訓  讓他知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The simple lesson that you cannot strong-arm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能強迫美國總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能淪落到跟他鬥氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't devolve to a pissing contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要給雷蒙德打電話  邀他來華盛頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna call Raymond. Invite him to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你徹底投降  否則他不會接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He won't accept anything but total surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm making the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把自己逼到那個地步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't put yourself in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道如何維護政府的尊嚴  謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know how to maintain the integrity of my office. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟總統待兩分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two minutes with the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克就能再獲青睞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Tusk may be back in his good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要阻止他們再度聯手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to disrupt the nuptials and prevent a second marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  你看上去棒極了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How are things?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  琳達讓我忙得腳不著地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Great. Linda works me to the bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這就是我想要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but that's what I signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  你幹得很不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, from what I've heard, you're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興能聽到這樣的評價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's really nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你談談特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I wanted to talk to you about Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定注意到她仍在適應自己的角色\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you've noticed that she's still sort of adjusting to her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.58,0:24:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說自信方面嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean her confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該主動去找她談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think it would be great if you reached out to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她知道如果有什麼需要你會幫助她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just let her know that you're there if there's anything that she needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實跟她不熟  我們見過  但是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't really know her that well. I mean, we've met, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.38,0:24:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者就告訴她  你很喜歡為總統工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe just tell her that you enjoy working for the president
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意盡你所能幫助她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you're there to be of help to her in any way you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.81,0:24:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你不覺得那樣有點唐突嗎    -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You don't think that's a little -- I don't know -- brash?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.79,0:24:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就這麼去找她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For me to just approach her like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.24,0:24:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:24:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《華盛頓先驅報》前僱員佐伊·巴恩斯加入頭條網
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.02,0:25:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}杜蘭特部門
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.42,0:25:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}羅素獲得黨鞭辦公室支援  競選州長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}議員得到副總統支援
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.81,0:25:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已接通斯克斯基宅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've reached the Skorsky residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.36,0:25:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請在嗶聲後留言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是湯姆·漢默施密特  還是要找簡寧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tom Hammerschmidt again. Still trying to reach Janine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.51,0:25:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是重要的事  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Still important. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.99,0:25:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:25:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢默施密特整天都在往我們新聞處打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hammerschmidt's been calling our press office all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:26:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一樣不希望鬧出任何新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want a story to come out any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.81,0:26:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則我們損失一名重要線人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We lose a major asset if it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.74,0:26:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能以安保理由讓他噤聲嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you squash it for security reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.17,0:26:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦讓媒體知道就不行了  第一修正案什麼的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not once it's been shared with the press. First Amendment crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.74,0:26:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牢房並沒能解決問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ward isn't making things any easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.89,0:26:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想邀個大功\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She wants a notch in her belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.83,0:26:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給她一個機會了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're giving her one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.13,0:26:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是古德溫  她想要奧爾西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not Goodwin. She wants Orsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.32,0:26:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六年的首要通緝犯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most Wanted list for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來搞定漢默施密特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll handle Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.56,0:26:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得確保古德溫認罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to make sure Goodwin takes the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35年刑期  不許假釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If 35 with no parole doesn't scare the piss out of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.58,0:26:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對能嚇倒他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what will.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.87,0:26:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去嚇唬他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then don't try to scare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.85,0:26:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他徹底絕望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remove hope from equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.44,0:26:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力控制這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried to keep this contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.58,0:26:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒預料到漢默施密特會出現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't anticipate Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯克斯基女士跟他合作了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is Ms. Skorsky cooperating with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.95,0:26:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他給她打過電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.25,0:26:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在聯調局的朋友說他們沒交談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My guy at the bureau said they haven't actually spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.75,0:26:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少沒在電話裡交談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least not on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.85,0:26:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果鬧上法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If this goes to court...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.14,0:27:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That won't happen, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.08,0:27:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他發表了文章就會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It will if he publishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.19,0:27:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來找你是因為我無法控制漢默施密特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm bringing this to you because I can't control Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.87,0:27:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.31,0:27:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要發動正面進攻  然後守住陣線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to invite a full-frontal attack. Then hold the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.41,0:27:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟他談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對面  只有我們倆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Face to face. Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得那不是個好主意  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think that's a good idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.87,0:27:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有更好的主意嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.32,0:27:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法避免戰爭  但我們可以選擇戰場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't avoid the battle, but we can choose the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.39,0:27:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把會面安排在白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.20,0:27:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擺架子嚇唬他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll intimidate him with formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.01,0:27:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.25,0:27:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你沒有耐心聽道歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you don't have patience for apologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.59,0:27:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我很抱歉讓你失望了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm sorry if I've let you down in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.99,0:27:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們集中精神解決眼前問題吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's concentrate on what's in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.79,0:27:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我安排好之後會告訴你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know when I have a time set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.10,0:27:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-越快越好    -是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Soon as possible.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.75,0:28:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是長篇報道的概述嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So this is a sort of outline to the larger piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.05,0:28:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題都在下一頁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With questions on the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在是私下談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.00,0:28:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  私下談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. Off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.44,0:28:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆  我知道你關心這個年輕人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, Tom, I know that you care about this young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也尊重你的職業精神\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I respect you as a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.29,0:28:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這些問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But these questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.83,0:28:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不直接問我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't you just ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.01,0:28:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不再掐死別人家寵物了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when I stopped strangling people's pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.67,0:28:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  羅素議員的死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, the death of Congressman Russo --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.29,0:28:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我的朋友  彼得·羅素\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean my friend, Peter Russo,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.54,0:28:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的自殺讓兩個年幼的孩子失去了父親\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whose suicide left two small children with no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.85,0:28:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不會回答關於那事的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I will not answer questions about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.79,0:28:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我知道  不  告訴她我待會兒回電\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes? I'm aware of that. No. Tell her I'll call her right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.17,0:29:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你兩分鐘  剛剛是杜蘭特國務卿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two minutes. Secretary Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.92,0:29:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以在外面等你給她回電\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can wait outside for you to call her back --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.14,0:29:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們說完\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, let's finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.90,0:29:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.13,0:29:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打算發表這些內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if you decide to print any of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真能找到願意發表的出版機構\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}assuming you find an outlet that's willing to,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.12,0:29:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  確實會讓我頭疼一陣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then, yes, it might cause me a headache for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.35,0:29:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會做出迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I will not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.99,0:29:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來  只會更加突出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I think it will only prove to highlight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.09,0:29:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德溫先生的論斷多麼可笑  我同情他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}how ridiculous Mr. Goodwin's claims are. I pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.91,0:29:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真心的  我覺得他需要幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I truly do. I think he needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.11,0:29:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我採訪過很多精神異常的人  他沒瘋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've interviewed many mentally ill people. He's not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.41,0:29:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議你把自己的文章再好好讀讀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I would suggest that you read your own article again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.94,0:29:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是非常痛苦  這兩者是有區別的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's distressed. There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.27,0:29:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解  看到他入獄對你打擊一定很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I understand. It must be a terrible blow to see him in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.66,0:29:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但湯姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But, Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.28,0:29:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋·波斯納確有其人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel Posner exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.71,0:29:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到她  但我已經證實她不是捏造的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't been able to find her, but I've proven she's not a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊·科佩尼科也是  這些人確實存在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The same goes for Roy Kapeniak. These people were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.38,0:29:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有社保號碼  既往住址...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They have social security numbers, past addresses, past --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.80,0:29:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全美各地的每個人都是如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And so does everyone from California to Maine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.77,0:29:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他們都有共謀嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have I conspired with all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.51,0:29:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得承認  酒駕問題確實有些解釋不清的細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to admit there are some troubling details regarding the DUI.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道  人們也是這麼說51區的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, people say the same thing about Area 51.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}有很多軍事及外星人傳聞的地區  美國政府對此既不肯定也不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.17,0:29:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以盡情想像\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can conjure up little gray men if you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:30:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了彼得·羅素嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you kill Peter Russo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.08,0:30:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆  你這就是自找沒趣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tom, you're embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.94,0:30:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了佐伊·巴恩斯嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you kill Zoe Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.86,0:30:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些荒唐事根本不值得我浪費這麼多時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've given you more time than this nonsense deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.02,0:30:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to ask these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.15,0:30:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我提問的話  我只問一句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, the only question I would ask is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.85,0:30:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的報道對古德溫先生有利還是有害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}does this sort of article hurt or help Mr. Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.21,0:30:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得做你認為對的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to do what you think is -- is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.75,0:30:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望你能理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I hope you can understand
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.13,0:30:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法認真對待這些問題  有損我的身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if I don't demean myself by taking any of it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.81,0:30:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您抽出時間  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I appreciate your time, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.91,0:30:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務完成了  把這事了結了吧  道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did my part. Now put it to bed, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.21,0:30:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會允許自己再面對這樣的處境\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't submit myself to this sort of exposure again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.91,0:30:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.49,0:30:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克和總統見面了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Has Tusk met with the president yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.39,0:30:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達說他們約了四點半\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda said they're meeting at 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.85,0:30:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫雷米  確保他上飛機前我能見他一面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Call Remy. Make sure he doesn't get on his plane before I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就去辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.90,0:31:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃剋夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mrs. Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.53,0:31:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想說  我非常榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to say how rewarding it's been,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.43,0:31:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在白宮西樓工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}working here in the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.58,0:31:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為您丈夫工作  我很自豪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm so proud to be working for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.10,0:31:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我知道他賞識你的勤奮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you. I know he appreciates all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.61,0:31:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我現在在他身邊工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, now that I'm working so closely with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.90,0:31:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼我能幫到您的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if there's anything I can do for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何能幫您或他減輕負擔的事...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}anything that would make yours or his life easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.80,0:31:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續做好你的工作就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just keep doing what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.04,0:31:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心的  您別客氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Truly, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.85,0:31:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓您知道  你們可以依靠我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to know you can rely on me. Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.33,0:31:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  謝謝  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know that. Thank you, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  沃剋夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Mrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.30,0:31:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-讓我來    -沒事  我手不太聽使喚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oh, here. Let me.   - Oh, it's just my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很難受嗎    -是啊  今晚估計要下雨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Are they bothering you?   - Yeah. Probably gonna get rain tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.90,0:32:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去開門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.56,0:32:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  繼續攪拌肉湯就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Um, no. Just, uh, keep the broth moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.89,0:32:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是聯調局的格林特工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Agent Green, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.54,0:32:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空嗎  斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you have a moment, Ms. Skorsky?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有  我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.43,0:32:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能進去嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.49,0:32:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得把爐子關了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just need to turn the stove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-待在這兒  媽媽    -是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Stay in here, Mom.   - Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.32,0:32:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這兒就是了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那一次嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only that once?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.16,0:32:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就沒見過他了  也沒回他電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I haven't seen him since, or returned his calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.22,0:32:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他幾次試圖聯繫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many times has he tried to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.54,0:32:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  大概八九次吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Eight or nine times, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.87,0:32:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後他消停了一段時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then he stopped after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.15,0:32:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提到過機器人希洛尼摩斯或嘉文·奧爾西嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did he mention anything about Hieronymus Bot or Gavin Orsay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.07,0:32:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我該找個律師來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I think I should talk to a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們並不懷疑你是同謀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right now you're not suspected of being an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你找律師  那我們就要考慮一下了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you call a lawyer, we might have to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.94,0:32:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他提到了個黑客    -希洛尼摩斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- He mentioned some hacker.   - Hieronymus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.45,0:33:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴他  聯繫那個人不是什麼好主意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told him I thought it was a bad idea to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.32,0:33:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他所持的論調嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you aware of what he's claiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.84,0:33:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.61,0:33:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本來在跟他合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you and he were working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.01,0:33:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他那套陰謀論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you believe in this conspiracy theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你收到了巴恩斯女士的私密照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That it was you who received explicit photos of Ms. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.78,0:33:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是真的吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is any of that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.61,0:33:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得跟我們回華盛頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need you to come back to D.C. with us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.39,0:33:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在聯邦檢察官的見證下簽署這份聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and sign this statement in the presence of the U.S. attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.53,0:33:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你們想讓我指證他說謊嗎    -他沒有嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You want me to call him a liar.   - Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.23,0:33:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這樣對他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't do that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.66,0:33:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還得和湯姆·漢默施密特談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We also need you to speak with Tom Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.38,0:33:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們  能別把我扯進來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know what? Please, can you just keep me out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.89,0:33:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那個黑客毫無瓜葛...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with the hacker or the...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.91,0:33:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯克斯基女士  我們願意相信你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Skorsky, we want to believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.41,0:33:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你寫下來我們就相信你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we will if you put all of it in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.33,0:33:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒犯罪  你們查錯人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's not a criminal. You're going after the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.95,0:33:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們認為你們能嚇唬我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you think that you can intimidate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我自己家這樣騷擾我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}harass me like this in my own home,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.24,0:33:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會提出正式投訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will file a formal complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.18,0:33:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你語氣越來越像他了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're starting to sound an awful lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.51,0:34:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不能逮捕我  我什麼都沒做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't arrest me. I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.21,0:34:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.81,0:34:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有權請律師  而且你們沒有逮捕令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a right to legal counsel, and you haven't presented a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以逮捕你  斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can arrest you, Ms. Skorsky,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.42,0:34:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以教唆網路恐怖主義的名義\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for abetting an act of cyber terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.77,0:34:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你接下來三年都耗在法庭裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who's going to take care of your mother while you're
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.70,0:34:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來照顧你母親呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}spending the next three years in courtrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.49,0:34:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您擡手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you please raise your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.65,0:34:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-密查姆就不用了    -先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No, Meechum.   - Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.38,0:34:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆  我知道你不想跟我握手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum. I know you don't want to shake my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.91,0:34:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就直接略過吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so we'll just skip that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.72,0:34:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統完全沒有提\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president didn't mention anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼要提  抓你個冷不丁更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would he? The better to catch you off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.71,0:34:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要提\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.50,0:34:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好避免不必要的衝突\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we can avoid unnecessary conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.03,0:34:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特可不會撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett's not a good liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正會說謊的人總是讓人覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The gift of a good liar is making people think
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.12,0:34:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他天生不會說謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you lack a talent for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.41,0:34:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遠比你瞭解他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know him far better than you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.31,0:34:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他天生會什麼  不會什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and so I know what talents he has and lacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.32,0:34:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但假設他確實說謊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But let's assume he did lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.87,0:35:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不擔心聯邦能源監管委員會的調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not intimidated by a FERC investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.93,0:35:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽證會還沒開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd have grid overload and brown-outs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.63,0:35:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現電網過載  燈火管制\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before you could even get a hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.15,0:35:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在蓄意擡高電價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are deliberately keeping electric prices at inflated rates,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.78,0:35:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是違法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.02,0:35:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是對自由市場的反應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I'm responding to free market.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是受監管的自由市場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A regulated free market.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.09,0:35:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼做  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why are you doing this, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.91,0:35:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米也這樣問過我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy asked me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.70,0:35:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是故意找我茬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're making this about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是針對你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This isn't personal, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.45,0:35:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源市場的健全是我唯一在乎的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The integrity of our energy markets is my only concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.08,0:35:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然是針對我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course it's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.87,0:35:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你說服加勒特不再與中國針鋒相對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I asked you personally to convince Garrett to pull back from China.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.84,0:35:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你偏偏跟我對著幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You personally chose not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還故意破壞峰會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You personally sabotaged the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.65,0:35:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我政治生涯中從未\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have never once in my political career
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.65,0:35:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還讓內閣把我逼上絕路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you personally advised the cabinet to push me up against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.67,0:35:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因私人感情而耽誤正事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}allow personal feelings to get in the way of pragmatic --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.95,0:35:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我耍花招  弗蘭克  我耍不動了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do not try and spin me, Frank. I am too old to tango.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.16,0:35:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I'll be blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.37,0:35:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受核能補助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Accept the subsidies
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.75,0:35:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則就面對能源委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or deal with FERC.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.55,0:35:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有第三條路可選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no third way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.54,0:35:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意想毀掉總統嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you intentionally trying to destroy the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想保護總統  免受你的傷害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to protect the president. From you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.05,0:36:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在為國務卿提名的事報復我吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about the secretary of state nomination, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.54,0:36:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是副總統了  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the vice president now, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.90,0:36:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會為陳年往事掉淚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't cry over what happened in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.97,0:36:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我力保你  你才當上副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're vice president because I vouched for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.29,0:36:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you had no other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.98,0:36:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是政治需要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Political necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.97,0:36:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你24小時做決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have 24 hours to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.02,0:36:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用送了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll show myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.07,0:36:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.83,0:36:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  這是克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, this is Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.08,0:36:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人  見到你很榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood, it is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.86,0:36:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子珍  很欣賞你最近做出的種種努力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jean-- my wife-- has been very taken with your recent efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.31,0:36:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天我一定要見見她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd like to meet her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.81,0:36:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她肯定非常願意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She would very much like that, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.13,0:36:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼看呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.46,0:36:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最近在做的事  你怎麼看呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are your thoughts about our recent efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.63,0:36:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防止不必要的暴力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh. I am in favor of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.57,0:36:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that prevents unnecessary violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.47,0:37:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's nice to meet you, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.65,0:37:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你今晚開球好運  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, good luck with that first pitch tonight, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.88,0:37:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次要投進本壘板  夫人再見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make it to the plate this time. Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.80,0:37:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這防彈背心真不舒服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This Kevlar is cooking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.77,0:37:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須得穿  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to use it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我練習時沒穿過  這下胳膊都轉不動了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I didn't practice with it, and now I can hardly rotate my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.40,0:37:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該提醒您的  對不起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should have mentioned it. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.73,0:37:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這球要是過不了本壘板  我拿你是問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If this ball doesn't make it over the plate, it's your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.39,0:37:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這兒幹什麼  沒事可做嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what are you doing here? Don't you have things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.94,0:37:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒來過卡姆登球場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never been to Camden Yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們  馬上將投出今晚第一球\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, here to throw out the first pitch tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有幸請上  美國副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we are honored to introduce the vice president of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.13,0:38:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  密查姆的球\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Boss, boss. Meechum's ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝  吉祥物呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much. Where's the mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.35,0:38:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱得真好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Beautifully done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.59,0:38:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.36,0:38:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚很熱  大家都想趕快看比賽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I know it's a hot night and you all want to get to the baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一投出這玩意兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So as soon as I throw this sucker,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.37,0:38:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家就喝點東西  享受比賽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}grab a drink, enjoy the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.33,0:38:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝兩隊好運\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and best of luck to both teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.94,0:38:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收回那句話  這是在卡姆登球場啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Scratch that. We're at Camden Yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.11,0:38:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金鶯隊加油\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go Orioles!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.77,0:39:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走  快走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.03,0:39:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說是控制節點的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm told the distribution line that controls
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.38,0:39:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配電線路造成了供電中斷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the pinch point caused the outages.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝科  你的一家公司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}BAPCO. One of your companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.00,0:39:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  電量出問題了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. There was a capacity issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.93,0:39:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人在以最快速度搶修\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're working as quickly as we can to resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三位州長給我打過電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I've got three governors calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院在用應急電源  你們最好儘快修理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hospitals on emergency power. So quickly better mean quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.68,0:40:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要2到3個小時  也許能快些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The latest estimate I got was two to three hours, maybe sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.10,0:40:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  這是故意的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, was this intentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.91,0:40:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我知道你最近不怎待見我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, I know you don't hold me in the highest regard at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.37,0:40:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你居然會這麼想  我很吃驚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I am alarmed that you could even entertain such a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這時候出現這種事讓人很難相信是巧合\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, the timing makes coincidence hard to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是熱浪的緣故  熱浪會讓電網達到使用極限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is a heat wave. That always pushes the grid to its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  快讓人們擺脫黑暗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get the people out of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.91,0:40:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每30分鐘報告一次進展情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Updates every 30 minutes on your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.64,0:40:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我要通知你  我明天可能要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should inform you, sir, that I may need to take
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.99,0:40:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關閉兩座電廠做不定期維修\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}two of my plants offline tomorrow for unscheduled maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.83,0:40:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  哪兩座廠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why? Which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.06,0:40:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐治亞州和田納西州\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Georgia and Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.59,0:40:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次停電使這兩座廠的負荷很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This blackout has put a great deal of stress on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.34,0:40:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工程師們擔心燃料棒密封條破損\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My engineers are concerned about the seals on the fuel rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.36,0:40:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼東南部也要斷電嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we're looking at outages on the southeast grid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.85,0:40:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能  幾天吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Could be. For a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.44,0:40:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, that's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.55,0:40:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全第一   我們不希望出事故\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Safety comes first. We don't want an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.54,0:40:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  詳細情況報告給琳達  儘快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get a full report to Linda, ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.02,0:40:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生  謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.87,0:41:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在耍花招\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's toying with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.96,0:41:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  或許真有這樣的安全問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, this could be a legitimate safety issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.94,0:41:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想奪回權力  那幾個電廠沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wants a seat back at the table. Those plants are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼這麼做  我們的確有分歧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why is he doing this? We've had our differences,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.52,0:41:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但非要做出這麼偏激的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but something drastic like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.52,0:41:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他說了能源委員會可能會展開聽證會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I did tell him about the possible FERC action.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.83,0:41:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.60,0:41:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打電話給我  我接了電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he called me. I answered the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.82,0:41:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不立即通知我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you inform me immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.84,0:41:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說你們的談話很有成效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He told me you had a productive talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.83,0:41:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他同意核能補助的事  我以為你們談妥了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That he was on board with the subsidy. I assumed everything was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.45,0:41:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提議進行新一輪貿易談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was proposing renewed trade talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.79,0:41:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本沒談核能補助的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We didn't talk about the subsidy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.63,0:41:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把我們倆都給耍了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's playing both of us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.64,0:41:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他說他同意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he told you he was on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.10,0:41:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼還提能源委員會的事呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}why'd you bring up FERC?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.40,0:41:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說這下我放心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told him I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.31,0:41:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他不答應  我們可要採取行動了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That we could have taken action if he didn't comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.28,0:41:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他是在套你的話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think he's fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想套出我們下一步行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To see what our next move might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.67,0:41:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think so, sir. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.00,0:41:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南部兩個發電廠的事他在說謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he is lying about those two plants in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.35,0:41:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能猜測  一定要確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we can't guess. We have to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.08,0:41:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓雷蒙德·塔斯克來做風險評估\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, do you want Raymond Tusk to assess that risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.95,0:41:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是政府來做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or the United States government?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.68,0:41:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我們接管他的電廠嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting we take over his facilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.94,0:41:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有過這樣的先例\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is precedent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.42,0:41:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伍德羅·威爾遜接管鐵路三年整\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Woodrow Wilson did it with the railroads for three full years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.39,0:41:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是戰爭時期\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In a time of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.16,0:42:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在危急時期  就像現在這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In a time of emergency, which is what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人民需要一位領袖  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The country needs a leader, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.76,0:42:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿足他們  別向雷蒙德·塔斯克屈服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give them one. Do not bend to Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.21,0:42:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.21,0:42:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過你可能不喜歡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said you might not like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.51,0:42:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我看起來像是瘋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It makes me seem crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.15,0:42:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最收斂的版本了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is the most toned-down version.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.15,0:42:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力用最和善的口吻  不摻入偏見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried to be as kind as I could without being biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.21,0:42:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不希望這報道公諸於眾吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think you want this going out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.01,0:42:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能和簡寧談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I talk to Janine?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.91,0:42:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓你離開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wants you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.35,0:43:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你說了謊    -盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You lied.   - Lucas...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.00,0:43:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙了湯姆  也騙了聯邦檢察官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You lied to Tom. You lied to the U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.54,0:43:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道還能怎麼辦    -說真話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I didn't know what else to do.   - Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.04,0:43:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會逮捕我  他們會讓我失去信譽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll arrest me. They'll discredit everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.11,0:43:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時  人們會像不相信你那樣不相信我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And nobody is going to believe me more than they believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.35,0:43:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們能讓公眾知道  讓人們產生疑問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we can get the story out there. Get people asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.94,0:43:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他們只會覺得我們倆都瘋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It'll just look like two crazy instead of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.88,0:43:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你打算自保\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you're saving yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.61,0:43:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護我們兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to save the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.75,0:43:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.82,0:43:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認罪吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.50,0:43:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是無罪的    -你不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I'm not guilty.   - You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.27,0:43:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你犯了罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.00,0:43:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-罪名還不只一項    -但不包括謀殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Multiple crimes.   - Not murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.28,0:43:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承認罪行  好好表現  早點出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take the plea. Be good. Get out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.50,0:44:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都坑我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everybody -- everybody's fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.51,0:44:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是想害你  就不會來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I was trying to fuck you I wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.38,0:44:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要逃脫罪責了  是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's gonna get away with it, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.43,0:44:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.93,0:44:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有加冰的茶嗎  給我一杯    -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Take an iced tea if you have any.   - We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.75,0:44:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不想總這樣偷偷摸摸的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish I didn't have to keep coming through back doors like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.17,0:44:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是不想讓新聞界的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we wouldn't want our friends in the fourth estate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.02,0:44:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道你來這裡嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to know you were here, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是你費了好大的功夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Especially since you've gone to such lengths
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.57,0:44:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直置身政治鬥爭之外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to remain above the fray of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.35,0:44:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能奪走發電廠  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't seize the plants, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.51,0:44:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒得手呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We haven't seized anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.04,0:44:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有這準備  但只要你合作就不會那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're ready to, but we won't if you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.39,0:44:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是違法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.38,0:45:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不違法  你心裡清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.49,0:45:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情況下  總統可以下達行政命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president can issue an executive order in times of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.61,0:45:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在法庭上據理力爭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll fight it in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.78,0:45:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那比能源委員會的調查更費時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which will take even longer than a FERC investigation would.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.14,0:45:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在此期間  你的發電廠無法盈利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And in the meantime, you make nothing from those plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.81,0:45:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.14,0:45:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡  我們達成了協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right here in this room, we agreed to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.78,0:45:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出了合作的承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We agreed as men of our word.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.60,0:45:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直信守承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I held up my end of that bargain
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.23,0:45:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你在法案的事上背信棄義\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}until you abandoned me on the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.37,0:45:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我讓雷米去協助你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I sent Remy to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.15,0:45:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是法案通過參議院之後  你之前可沒幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After I got it passed through the Senate with no help from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.49,0:45:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和總統鬧僵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to protect my relationship with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.90,0:45:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯波特瑟爾韋尼亞峰會期間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then you tried to use me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.88,0:45:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還企圖利用我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}during the summit in Spotsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.49,0:45:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我活著不是為了做你最好的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was not put on this earth to be your best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.82,0:45:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是為了和你分享我的所有情報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or to share every piece of information I have with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.97,0:45:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是達成了互利共贏的合作關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We agreed to a mutually beneficial partnership. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.76,0:45:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  而我現在發現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. And what's become very clear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.89,0:45:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你合作對我沒有任何好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is that I benefit in no way from this partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.54,0:45:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不裝傻了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's not pretend to be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.88,0:45:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最看重的都是個人利益\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We both respect self-interest above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.18,0:46:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在  雙方利益不再一致\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our versions of that no longer align.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.57,0:46:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要犯下無法挽回的錯誤了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are on the verge of making an irreversible mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.48,0:46:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.06,0:46:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確可能是在犯錯  誰知道呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I may well be making a mistake. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.48,0:46:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道你會聯繫琳達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I do know is that you'll be calling Linda
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.18,0:46:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她你接受核能補助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and telling her that you'll accept the subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.83,0:46:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有錢  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You may have all the money, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.81,0:46:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I have all the men with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.45,0:46:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是設好號碼的一次性電話  她在等你答覆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a burner, pre-dialed. She's expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.05,0:46:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這是昨晚的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, and, uh, yes. From last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.84,0:46:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按行話說  現在輪到你發球了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The ball's in your court, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.53,0:47:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝  你嚇死我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jesus Christ. You scared the shit outta me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.50,0:47:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼隨隨便便地喊上帝嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you supposed to take the lord's name in vain like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.37,0:47:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續開著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Leave it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.50,0:47:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電費太貴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It costs too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.89,0:47:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會付的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.38,0:47:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德溫認罪了  他要進監獄了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodwin took the plea. He's going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.17,0:47:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一切都結束了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So does that mean this is all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.18,0:47:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我們還是要小心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. We still have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.73,0:47:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  沒有他  就不會有人找我了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But why? If he's gone, then nobody's looking for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.23,0:47:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我們所知沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not that we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.20,0:47:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在確保萬無一失之前  一切照常\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until we know, nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.60,0:47:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你來就是為了讓我空歡喜一場嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what, you just came over here to get my hopes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.61,0:47:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來是為了確保你今晚不去教堂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I came here to make sure that you don't go to church tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.19,0:47:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want to fuck me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.67,0:47:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這才是你的本意吧    -不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Is that what this is all about?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.36,0:47:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前幹過我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.86,0:47:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.20,0:48:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.24,0:48:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向能察覺男人對我的慾望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If there's one thing I know, it's when a man wants me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.49,0:48:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在教會得知了拉結的故事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I learned who Rachel was in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.49,0:48:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}拉結是《聖經》中和瑞秋同名的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.84,0:48:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她年輕漂亮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She was young and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.88,0:48:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各在她照看羊喝水時愛上了她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jacob fell in love with her while she was watering a lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.64,0:48:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做了七年的工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And she became his wife after he worked seven years
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.13,0:48:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才終於娶到她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to earn her hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.22,0:48:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉結有個叫約瑟的兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel had one son. Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.34,0:48:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來他成了國王\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He became a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.39,0:49:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你餓不餓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you hungry?
